  <brief_title>The Effects of Local Infiltration Versus Epidural Following Liver Resection 2</brief_title>
  <acronym>LIVER 2</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomised Trial of Peri-operative Nerve Block and Continuous Infusion of Local Anaesthetic Via Wound Catheter Versus Epidural in Patients Undergoing Open Liver Resection.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
